{"tid":1455464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警記者會真係睇到好心寒","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:11:30.000Z","uid":93540,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"35c96ea518c6dac014297d9faabc1e2655ed620e","tid":1455464,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:02:36.000Z","msg":"明知佢地都係兜圈9up 但都去左睇<br />\n最心寒係呢幾隻狗 表面上懶有禮貌解答人問題<br />\n但實際上就係事實已經擺係眼前<br />\n都仲要用唔同方法去彎曲事實 維護自己 抺黑勇武<br />\n到底佢地係點講得出口 完全唔撚覺得羞恥<br />\n權力使人腐化<br />\n我眼中係睇到一班為左錢 私慾埋沒自己人性既畜生<br />\n黑警冇一個係無辜 香港警察呢個名詞會遺臭萬年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7ca056692fb328077772335e77f6c1e2309d0d99","tid":1455464,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"8792495a9d18b626ade6b43752c2cbe3cbe6d188","tid":1455464,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d73d2a5f9ca039b9dee84d61903f9dc9d6b58fd7","tid":1455464,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:06:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"a9083ef60c1cf7dfb6a034492d010bd870874095","tid":1455464,"uid":93540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:07:48.000Z","msg":"特別姓江果隻四眼狗 講野串撚到<br />\n擘大眼講大話 大大聲聲講歪理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe9dd75b35422f3ddecaa63750efde8ad1204ad","tid":1455464,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></sp